query:
-- 更新项目的assetsBaseUrl
UPDATE projects 
SET assetsBaseUrl = 'https://assets.ezcto.fun/openclaw-wzms'
WHERE id = 870001;

-- 更新logo的fileUrl
UPDATE assets 
SET fileUrl = 'https://assets.ezcto.fun/openclaw-wzms/assets/logo-86f6d46c.png'
WHERE projectId = 870001 AND assetType = 'logo';
